'''第二次提克里特之戰'''於2015年3月2日－4月17日進行，伊拉克安全部隊及反伊斯蘭國民兵擊敗[[伊斯兰国|伊斯兰国]]武裝分子，收復[[萨拉赫丁省|萨拉赫丁省]]首府[[提克里特|提克里特]]。

==戰役前準備==
2015年2月初，伊拉克部隊與盟友開始準備進攻提克里特，並於附近的[[薩邁拉|薩邁拉]]集結部隊。<ref>{{cite news|title=Iraqi forces prepare for Tikrit offensive|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/iraqi-forces-prepare-for-tikrit-offensive/2015/02/21/f05fd9f1-8892-4207-a212-029c94ed9c4e_story.html|accessdate=3 March 2015|agency=Washington Post|date=21 February 2015|work=The Washington Post|first=Loveday|last=Morris}}</ref>

以人數計，參與行動的聯軍部隊大部分是什葉派民兵。<ref name="washingtonpost.com">{{cite news|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/world/middle_east/iraqi-forces-battle-islamic-state-in-streets-of-strategic-tikrit/2015/03/11/a0dca5c0-c778-11e4-aa1a-86135599fb0f_story.html |script-title=en:Iraqi forces break militants’ hold on Tikrit in major battle against Islamic State|work=Washington Post|accessdate=12 March 2015|first=Erin|last=Cunningham|date=11 March 2015}}</ref><ref name="news.yahoo.com">{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/top-us-general-optimistic-outcome-tikrit-battle-052414345--politics.html|title=Top US general optimistic about outcome of Tikrit battle|date=7 March 2015|work=Yahoo News|accessdate=12 March 2015}}</ref>

戰役開始前，提克里特的居民大多數已逃到庫爾德族自治區或巴格達等地。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/04/opinion/tikrit-battle-opinion |title=Why 'emotional' battle for Tikrit will defeat ISIS - CNN.com |publisher=Edition.cnn.com |date=2015-03-04 |accessdate=2015-03-14}}</ref>聯合國估計自針對伊斯蘭國的攻勢開始後，約28,000名平民已逃至[[薩邁拉|薩邁拉]]。<ref name="BBC: Thousands flee ">{{cite news|title=Islamic State crisis: Thousands flee Iraqi advance on Tikrit|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-31753727|accessdate=5 March 2015|agency=BBC News|date=5 March 2015|archive-date=2019-04-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190407045856/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-31753727|dead-url=no}}</ref>

戰役開始時，以美國為首的多國聯盟未有參與收復提克里特的行動。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.presstv.ir/Detail/2015/03/11/401357/Center-of-Tikrit-liberated|title=PressTV-Center of Tikrit liberated|publisher=|accessdate=12 March 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.cbsnews.com/news/iraq-iran-shiite-isis-tikrit-kirkuk-but-only-us-airstrikes-in-tikrit/|title=Iraq battles ISIS in Tikrit, Kirkuk, but only has U.S. help in 1 fight|date=10 March 2015|publisher=|accessdate=12 March 2015|work=CBS News}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://time.com/3740043/tikrit-isis-iraq-iran-shia-battle/ |script-title=en:ISIS Loses Tikrit to Iraqi Troops and Shi‘ite Militias|author=Sabrina Toppa|work=TIME.com|accessdate=12 March 2015|date=11 March 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-31833592|title=BBC News - Islamic State conflict: US predicts Iraqi victory in Tikrit|work=BBC News|accessdate=12 March 2015|date=11 March 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thenews.com.pk/Todays-News-1-306620-Iraqi-forces-enter-IS-held-Tikrit-after-10-day-push |title=Iraqi forces enter IS-held Tikrit after 10-day push |publisher=Thenews.com.pk |date=2015-03-07 |accessdate=2015-03-14}}</ref>

==進攻==

===包圍===
2015年3月2日，伊拉克政府發起旨在收復提克里特的大規模軍事行動，<ref>{{cite web|title=Iraq moves against Islamic State in Tikrit|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-31689433|website=BBC News|publisher=BBC|accessdate=2 March 2015|archive-date=2019-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190408021944/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-31689433|dead-url=no}}</ref>出動 20,000－30,000人和空軍，從三面進攻提克里特。<ref name="Iraqi forces assault Tikrit">{{cite web|url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/124259/World/Region/UPDATED-Iraq-forces-take-on-Tikrit-in-biggest-oper.aspx |title=UPDATED: Iraq forces take on Tikrit in biggest operation yet - Region - World - Ahram Online |publisher=English.ahram.org.eg |date= |accessdate=2015-03-14}}</ref>

伊斯蘭國武裝分子在通往提克里特的各條路徑佈下大量[[簡易爆炸裝置|簡易爆炸裝置]]，並部署大量狙擊手，引致聯軍進展緩慢。<ref name="The Long War Journal: Iran">{{cite news|title=Iranian-backed Shiite militias lead Iraq’s fight to retake Tikrit|url=http://www.longwarjournal.org/archives/2015/03/iranian-backed-shiite-militias-lead-iraqs-fight-to-retake-tikrit.php|accessdate=4 March 2015|agency=The Long War Journal|date=4 March 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|title=ISIL militants slow Tikrit advance with bombs and snipers|url=http://www.thenational.ae/world/middle-east/isil-militants-slow-tikrit-advance-with-bombs-and-snipers|accessdate=4 March 2015|agency=The National|date=4 March 2015|archive-date=2016-08-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160830023914/http://www.thenational.ae/world/middle-east/isil-militants-slow-tikrit-advance-with-bombs-and-snipers|dead-url=no}}</ref>

3月9日，聯軍攻佔提克里特東北方的Al-Alam，切斷守軍與伊拉克北部伊斯蘭國控制區的最後陸上聯繫，完成對提克里特的包圍。伊斯蘭國武裝分子傷亡慘重，<ref name="presstv.ir"/>防守提克里特的戰士僅餘下2,000－3,000人。<ref name="grip">{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/31/world/middleeast/un-leader-warns-iraq-not-to-mistreat-civilians-after-liberation-from-isis.html|title=Islamic State’s Grip on City Appears Firmer Than Iraqis Acknowledge|date=31 March 2015|work=The New York Times|accessdate=27 May 2016}}</ref><ref name="presstv.ir">{{cite web|url=http://www.newsweek.com/isis-escalate-ramadi-attacks-iraqi-forces-induce-tikrit-losses-312945 |title=Facing Defeat in Tikrit, ISIS Escalates Attacks Closer to Baghdad |publisher=Newsweek.com |accessdate=2015-03-14}}</ref>

===攻入市區===
地面的攻城行動於3月11日開始。<ref name="appearstostall">{{cite web|url=http://english.alarabiya.net/en/News/middle-east/2015/03/13/Iraqi-offensive-on-Tikrit-appears-to-stall.html|title=Iraqi offensive on Tikrit appears to stall|publisher=|accessdate=31 March 2015}}</ref>政府官員次日宣稱已收復四分之三城區。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/wires/afp/article-2991325/Iraq-forces-say-wont-rushed-final-Tikrit-assault.html |title=Iraqi forces poised for final Tikrit assault - Yahoo News |publisher=News.yahoo.com |date= 15 March 2015|accessdate=2015-03-14 |location=London}}</ref><ref name="independent1">{{cite news|author=Qassim Abdul-Zahra |url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/war-with-isis-iraq-government-claims-that-most-of-tikrit-is-liberated-10104956.html |title=War with Isis: Iraq government claims most of Tikrit is liberated - Middle East - World |publisher=Independent.co.uk |date=2014-03-19 |accessdate=2015-03-14 |location=London}}</ref><ref name="edition.cnn.com">{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2015/03/12/middleeast/iraq-isis-tikrit/ |title=Iraqi forces retake most of Tikrit from ISIS, militia leader says |publisher=Edition.cnn.com |date= |accessdate=2015-03-14}}</ref>

3月13日，據報伊斯蘭國仍然控制該市的一半部分，地面攻勢受阻。<ref name="appearstostall"/>到3月14日，在市中心的伊斯蘭國分子據報已減至1,000人左右。<ref name="Tikrit campaign stalls">{{cite web|url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2015/03/19/the-big-offensive-against-isis-in-tikrit-has-stalled.html|title=The Big Offensive Against ISIS in Tikrit Has Stalled|work=The Daily Beast|accessdate=22 March 2015}}</ref>等待援軍的伊拉克部隊暫時停止推進。<ref>{{cite news|url=https://www.reuters.com/article/2015/03/15/us-mideast-crisis-iraq-idUSKBN0MB0MD20150315|title=Iraqi offensive on Tikrit stalls, Kurds say Islamists used chlorine|publisher=Reuters|accessdate=22 March 2015|date=15 March 2015}}</ref>

===聯盟空襲===
美國要求由伊朗人領導的什葉派民兵退出提克里特戰鬥，然後才會在提克里特提供空中支援。伊拉克政府接受美國的條件。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.npr.org/2015/03/26/395604508/after-weeks-on-the-sidelines-u-s-begins-air-campaign-in-tikrit|title=After Weeks On The Sidelines, U.S. Begins Air Campaign In Tikrit|date=26 March 2015|work=NPR.org|accessdate=27 May 2016}}</ref>

3月25日，以美國為首的聯盟開始空襲提克里特的伊斯蘭國目標。<ref name="US launches first airstrikes in Tikrit">{{cite web|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-32035340|title=Islamic State conflict: US launches Tikrit air strikes|work=BBC News|accessdate=2016-06-22|archive-date=2019-03-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190306180326/https://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-32035340|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/03/26/world/middleeast/iraq-islamic-state-tikrit-united-states-airstrikes.html | work=The New York Times | first1=Rod | last1=Nordland | first2=Peter | last2=Baker | title=Opening New Iraq Front, U.S. Strikes ISIS in Tikrit | date=25 March 2015}}</ref>該夜美軍在提克里特的中心進行17次空襲。<ref name="OIR airstrike updates">{{cite web|url=http://www.defense.gov/home/features/2014/0814_iraq/Airstrikes6.html|title=Map of Countires Supporting the Proliferation Security Initiative|publisher=|accessdate=31 March 2015|archive-date=2015-07-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150714065710/http://www.defense.gov/home/features/2014/0814_iraq/Airstrikes6.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>地面上的聯軍原定於同日再度發動進攻，但是因為內部意見分歧而推遲兩日。<ref name="nowhere">{{cite web|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/iraqi-volunteers-fighting-tikrit-say-army-nowhere-be-found-1861242|title=Iraqi Volunteers Fighting For Tikrit Say The Army Is Nowhere To Be Found|date=27 March 2015|work=International Business Times|accessdate=31 March 2015}}</ref>

3月27日，參戰的什葉派民兵大部分已退出提克里特的戰鬥。<ref name="Shiite militias pull out">{{cite web|url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2015/03/shia-militias-step-joins-battle-tikrit-150327010352355.html|title=Shia militias pull back as US joins battle for Tikrit|publisher=|accessdate=31 March 2015}}</ref>

3月28日，以美國為首的聯盟在提克里特及附近進行了8次空襲。<ref name="defense">{{cite web | url=http://www.defense.gov/news/newsarticle.aspx?id=128482 | title=Airstrikes Continue Against ISIL in Syria, Iraq | publisher=U.S Department  of Defense | accessdate=29 March 2015}}</ref>

===攻入市中心===
3月31日，伊拉克安全部隊進入市中心，<ref name="entry into central Tikrit">{{cite web|url=http://www.aol.com/article/2015/03/31/iraq-premier-troops-in-center-of-islamic-state-held-tikrit/21159730/|title=Iraq premier: Troops in center of Islamic State-held Tikrit - AOL.com|work=AOL Article|accessdate=31 March 2015}}</ref>攻佔省政府總部和提克里特醫院。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://uk.businessinsider.com/afp-iraq-forces-retake-government-hq-in-tikrit-from-is-2015-3?r=US#ixzz3Vy4uo8zB|title=Iraqi forces retake government HQ in Tikrit from ISIS - Business Insider|date=31 March 2015|work=Business Insider|accessdate=31 March 2015}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|url=http://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKBN0MR1G420150331?sp=true|title=Iraqi forces drive Islamic State out of central Tikrit: PM|publisher=|accessdate=31 March 2015|work=Reuters|date=31 March 2015|archive-date=2015-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150402175419/http://ca.reuters.com/article/topNews/idCAKBN0MR1G420150331?sp=true|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

4月2日，伊拉克部隊收復更多地方，包括前總統薩達姆的官邸。<ref name="ISIL holds on">{{cite news |url=http://mobile.nytimes.com/2015/04/03/world/middleeast/isis-forces-pushed-out-of-tikrit.html |title=Iraq Forces, Pushing ISIS Out of Tikrit, Give Few Thanks for U.S. Airstrikes|publisher=|accessdate=2016-05-27}}</ref>

===肅清市內殘餘抵抗===
[[File:Captured_ISIL_fighter_in_Saladin_Governorate_(4).jpg|thumb]]

4月4日，市內局勢據報已經穩定下來。<ref name="Tikrit freed but in ruins">{{cite web|url=http://news.yahoo.com/iraqs-tikrit-free-islamic-state-city-ruins-060428880.html|title=Iraq's Tikrit, free of the Islamic State, is a city in ruins|date=4 April 2015|work=Yahoo News|accessdate=10 April 2015}}</ref>不過在4月5日有報道指城內仍有500名伊斯蘭國成員在數處持續抵抗。<ref name="hundreds">{{cite web|url=http://rudaw.net/english/middleeast/iraq/05042015|title=Hundreds of ISIS fighters, suicide bombers holed up in Tikrit district|work=Rudaw|accessdate=10 April 2015}}</ref>在接下來的數天戰鬥持續。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/04/09/world/middleeast/iraq-isis-offensive.html|title=Iraq Starts Drive Against ISIS, but Reports on Scale Differ|date=9 April 2015|work=The New York Times|accessdate=27 May 2016}}</ref>4月7日，一間設置了[[詭雷|詭雷]]陷阱的房屋爆炸，在提克里特領導反爆炸品部門的Thamer al-Hamdani-{准}-將喪生。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iraqinews.com/iraq-war/salahuddin-anti-explosives-director-killed-booby-trapped-house-explosion-north-tikrit/|title=Salahuddin anti-explosives director killed in booby-trapped house explosion north of Tikrit|work=Iraq news |accessdate=10 April 2015}}</ref>在4月7日至8日，據報有79名伊斯蘭國分子在提克里特被殺。<ref name="96 killed in Baiji and Tikrit">{{cite web|url=http://www.presstv.ir/Video/2015/04/07/405140/Iraqi-army-braces-for-liberation-of-Salahuddin-from-ISIL|title=PressTV|publisher=|accessdate=10 April 2015|archive-date=2015-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150413061402/http://www.presstv.ir/Video/2015/04/07/405140/Iraqi-army-braces-for-liberation-of-Salahuddin-from-ISIL|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.iraqinews.com/iraq-war/security-forces-kill-9-isis-militants-central-tikrit/|title=Security forces kill 9 ISIS militants in central Tikrit|work=Iraq news |accessdate=10 April 2015}}</ref><ref name="April 8 deaths">{{cite web|url=http://www.iraqinews.com/iraq-war/34-isis-elements-hiding-north-tikrit-killed/|title=34 ISIS elements killed in Tikrit|work=Iraq news |accessdate=10 April 2015}}</ref>

4月12日，伊拉克政府宣佈提克里特市內已經沒有伊斯蘭國分子存在。不過安全部隊於4月17日在市內發現匿藏的130名伊斯蘭國分子，並予以殲滅。<ref name=isbn9781440849879>{{Cite book |url=https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=A_w2DAAAQBAJ&pg=PA170 |title=ISIS: An Introduction and Guide to the Islamic State |page=170 |author=Brian L. Steed |publisher=ABC-CLIO |year=2016 |isbn=9781440849879}}</ref>

==傷亡==
3月20日，據報已有1,000名政府一方的戰鬥人員在戰役的早期階段陣亡。<ref name="stalled">{{cite web|url=http://www.mcclatchydc.com/2015/03/20/260513/operation-to-retake-tikrit-from.html|title=ISTANBUL: Operation to retake Tikrit from Islamic State stalled by heavy casualties, discord - Iraq - McClatchy DC|work=McClatchy DC|accessdate=22 March 2015|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150515080922/http://www.mcclatchydc.com/2015/03/20/260513/operation-to-retake-tikrit-from.html|archive-date=2015-05-15|dead-url=yes}}</ref>本次攻勢的指揮官Abdul al-Wahab al-Saadi中將表示直至3月30日已有450－750名伊斯蘭國武裝分子被殺。<ref name="grip"/>

